The paper discusses the relationship between SKOS concepts and natural language concepts, and uses Natural Language Processing techniques for analysis. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Deep Learning (cs.DL), or Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Among these, cs.IR and cs.CL are the most likely categories as they directly relate to the use of NLP techniques for analysis of KOSs. cs.AI, cs.DL, and cs.LG are also possible categories as they involve the use of AI and machine learning techniques, which are relevant to the study.
